---

# Release

```bash
make release VERSION=X.Y.Z
```

Runs [`scripts/release.sh`](scripts/release.sh): Formula bump → tag/push → build archives → `gh release create` → pin Formula revision.

```bash
make release-dry VERSION=X.Y.Z
make dist-arm64 VERSION=X.Y.Z
make release VERSION=X.Y.Z ARCHS=arm64,amd64,universal
```

Do not re-derive this in chat. Fix the script if broken. Release scope excludes install/services.
